Q1. Suppose you have a Cyber Security Center. Write a C++ program that takes
a complete name (first and last name) in a char array and user phone number in an
int array and displays his/her first name with a hello message along phone
number. display half of the number digits for security purposes.
Example:
Enter Your Name: Muhammad Murtaza
Enter your Cell #: 03080143575

Welcome To Murtaza's Security Hub
Hello Muhammad!
03425*****4
